descriptionHtml:
Gatti 09 Reina Armor for CBBEv3
--------------------------------------------------------------
I am not good at English. 
So enough support is not possible, please understand it.
Its my 10th MOD.

The female Heavy/Light armor \'Reina\' include Armor,Boots,Gauntlets and Shield.
Design inspration from \'Queens Blade\'.

Craftable. \'Studded\' Category.

Not support weight slider, only one size.(only neck adjusted)

---------------------------------------------------------------
Required
Caliente for Caliente\'s Body Mod - Big Bottom Edition v3

---------------------------------------------------------------
History
v1.2 Fix : Problem of arm mesh at 1st person view.
V1.1 Fix : Explosion armor mesh on midium slide body.
V1.0 Release.
